# SKILL: DEPENDENCY TRACER

## Purpose
Systematically trace all dependencies of a given code element (function, class, module, type) in both directions — what it depends on (downstream) and what depends on it (upstream).

## Activation
Use this skill when:
- About to modify a function/class/interface
- Need to understand blast radius of a change
- Investigating why a change in file A broke file Z
- Planning a refactoring that involves moving or renaming code

## Procedure

### DOWNSTREAM TRACE (What does this code depend on?)

### UPSTREAM TRACE (What depends on this code?)

